{"members":[{"header_text":" فس،  [تفسير  القمي ] : ","body_text":" <quranic_text>«وَ قَضَيْنٰا اِلَيْهِ ذٰلِكَ الْاَمْرَ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[الحجر۶۶]</footnote> اَيْ اَعْلَمْنَاهُ <quranic_text>«اَنَّ دٰابِرَ هٰؤُلاٰءِ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[الحجر۶۶]</footnote> يَعْنِي قَوْمَ لُوطٍ <quranic_text>«لَعَمْرُكَ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[الحجر۷۲]</footnote> اَيْ وَ حَيَاتِكَ يَا مُحَمَّدُ فَهَذِهِ فَضِيلَةٌ لِرَسُولِ اللَّهِ صَلَّي اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ الِهِ عَلَي الْاَنْبِيَاءِ.","translation":"","aligned_body":"TAG_OPEN:quranic_text وَ قَضَيْنٰا اِلَيْهِ ذٰلِكَ الْاَمْرَ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote الحجر ۶۶ TAG_CLOSE:footnote اَيْ اَعْلَمْنَاهُ TAG_OPEN:quranic_text اَنَّ دٰابِرَ هٰؤُلاٰءِ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote الحجر ۶۶ TAG_CLOSE:footnote يَعْنِي قَوْمَ لُوطٍ TAG_OPEN:quranic_text لَعَمْرُكَ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote الحجر ۷۲ TAG_CLOSE:footnote اَيْ وَ حَيَاتِكَ يَا مُحَمَّدُ فَهَذِهِ فَضِيلَةٌ لِرَسُولِ اللَّهِ صَلَّي اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ الِهِ عَلَي الْاَنْبِيَاءِ"}],"body_consensus_columns":[{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قضينا","display":"قَضَيْنٰا"},{"kind":"word","token":"اليه","display":"اِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ذلك","display":"ذٰلِكَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الامر","display":"الْاَمْرَ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"الحجر","display":"الحجر"},{"kind":"word","token":"۶۶","display":"۶۶"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"اي","display":"اَيْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"اعلمناه","display":"اَعْلَمْنَاهُ"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"ان","display":"اَنَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"دابر","display":"دٰابِرَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"هؤلاء","display":"هٰؤُلاٰءِ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","to